summary: I\'ve been stuck with ebony armor for a long time now so I decided to create a high definition version of it. The result is quite nice :)
descriptionHtml:
This is not a finished version. All thats been done is the main body armor. I have uni exams this week so I\'ll finish the entire rest of the ebony set next week.

The package replaces 4 textures all of the main body plate. It is very high res at 4096x4096... which I will probably scale down when i package with the complete set next week.

To install simply extract the contents to your skyrim folder.
author: eXtacy
